\c 23
\s Jehovha mufudzi wangu
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha mufudzi wangu\x + Isa. 40.11. Eze. 34.23. Joh. 10.11.\x*; handishaiwi\x + VaFir. 4.19.\x*.
\v 2 Anondirarisa pamafuro manyoro\x + Eze. 34.14. Joh. 10.9.\x*; anondisesedza pamvura inozorodza\x + Map. 31.3. Isa. 40.11. 49.10. Zvak. 7.17.\x*.
\v 3 Anovandudza mweya wangu; anondisesedza panzira dzekururama\x + Map. 5.8. 31.3. 139.10,24. 143.10.\x* nekuda kwezita rake\x + Map. 25.11.\x*.
\v 4 Hongu, kunyange ndikafamba nemumupata\x + Map. 138.7.\x* wemumvuri werufu\x + Job. 3.5.\x*, handingatyi chakaipa\x + Map. 3.6. 27.1,3. 118.6.\x*, nokuti imwi muneni; tsvimbo yenyu nemudonzvo wenyu, ndizvo zvinondinyaradza\x + Isa. 43.2.\x*.
\v 5 Munogadzira tafura mberi kwangu\x + Map. 78.19. Zvir. 9.2. Job. 36.16. Map. 69.22.\x* pamberi pevavengi vangu\x + Map. 31.19.\x*; munozodza musoro wangu nemafuta\x + Map. 133.2. Mup. 9.8. Mat. 6.17. Ruk. 7.46. Map. 92.10.\x*; mukombe wangu unopfachuka\x + Map. 16.5.\x*.
\v 6 Zvirokwazvo kunaka nenyasha zvichanditevera mazuva ese eupenyu hwangu; uye ndichagara mumba maJehovha kusvika paurefu hwemazuva.